        <div class="service-page-content">
            <article class="service-main">

                <p class="speakable-answer">A <strong>khula lawyer in Karachi</strong> helps a Muslim wife dissolve her
                    marriage through the Family Court when living together has become impossible, even if the husband
                    refuses. MR Law Associates is led by Advocate Reema Jawed, a female family lawyer who files khula
                    petitions under the Family Courts Act 1964, handles the plaint, the summons to your husband, the
                    reconciliation stage, and the final decree, and stays beside you until the union council issues your
